text:
Hi,

This is due to the way percentages are calculated.
Here is a patch that fixes the problem.

--- agent/mibgroup/ucd-snmp/disk_hw.c   2011-08-31 11:22:10.000000000 +0100
+++ agent/mibgroup/ucd-snmp/disk_hw.c   2011-08-31 11:28:27.000000000 +0100
@@ -245,7 +245,7 @@


  static int _percent( int value, int total ) {
-    return (int)( value * 100 ) / total;
+    return (int)( value / (total / 100));
  }

  static netsnmp_fsys_info **

Many thanks

David
